title: Do you know what it means
creator: FuFio Cat

extendedInfo.description: Do You Know What It Means to Miss New Orleans is a song written by Eddie DeLange and Louis Alter, which was first heard in the movie New Orleans in 1947.        This is an arrangement for piano solo that you can play, set as ringtone and save the following files onto SD Card:         1) partiture in MIDI format;        2) music sheet in PDF and MSCZ (Muse Score) format;        4) song in MP3;SEARCH ON /SDCARD/MEDIA THIS FILES AFTER CLICK ON "SAVE" BUTTON!!!!        For simple improvisation you can alternate major (C-D-Eb-E-G-A) and minor (C-Eb-F-Gb-G-Bb) blues scale.        PDF sheet is written according to notation explained by Learn Jazz Chords android application you can download from market.Hope you enjoy with this jazz blues song!!piano blues jazz music play sheet arrangement
